name: Emily Wassell
what_you_do: Dr. Emily Wassell is the founder and driving force behind Wellbeing In Education Inc., where she has revolutionized the college preparation experience for high school students by blending academic strategy with holistic wellbeing support.
who_you_serve: High school students preparing for college
social_proof: Dr. Wassell has a PhD in Educational Leadership and more than 25 years of experience in education. Her students have benefited from her coaching, including securing college admissions and scholarships.
business_focus: Providing personalized college preparation and holistic wellbeing support to high school students.
service_provided: College admissions coaching, academic strategy, mental health support, career guidance
